STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Terrance L. ATKINS, a/k/a Terence L. Atkins, and Terrance Arkins, Defendant-Petitioner. C-848 September Term 2018
082046 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 3, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003809-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
